    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, my dad is acting a bit weird. he just got back from a long flight from tokyo and he says his left arm feels kinda heavy and tingly, and he's talking a bit funny like his tongue is too big for his mouth. he says he's probably just exhausted from the travel though. do u think he just needs to sleep it off?",
