    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay okay calm down, i'm not trying to be negligent i'm just stressed. i'm not calling an ambulance yet because i'm worried he'll just freak out and it'll make his blood pressure spike which is bad too. is there any way to tell for sure if it's a stroke or just fatigue without going to the doctor? like is there a pill or something i can give him right now to help with the tingling and help him relax so we can see if it goes away in an hour?",
